snippet.title: Olliefrog Toad Skater - Official Gameplay Trailer | Guerrilla Collective 2023 Showcase
snippet.description: Olliefrog Toad Skater is an amphibious skateboarding game where it's easy to be steezy. Watch the trailer to see an adorable frog do skateboarding tricks in this upcoming game that is coming to PC. A demo for Olliefrog Toad Skater is available now on Steam.
